  Changelog:
  v1.0.0 - Initial release with customized stack sizes for all categories.
  v1.0.1 - Updated Layout to reflect entire item categories for ease of use and additional customization.

  Compatibility:
  - Compatible with 7 Days to Die Alpha 1.0 Stable 
  - Server Side Compatable, no need for client install.

  Notes and Warnings:
  - Ensure that no other mods conflict with stack size modifications.
  - Recommended game settings: Survival mode, difficulty set to Warrior.
